@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### GET /users — list all users (UserService is a singleton injected by DI)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

###

### GET /users/:id — find user by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1

###

### GET /users/:id — not found
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/999

###

### GET /whoami — request-scoped provider reads X-Request-Id header
GET {{baseUrl}}/whoami
X-Request-Id: abc-123

###

### GET /whoami — no header, returns "none"
GET {{baseUrl}}/whoami
